name: 100 Daily UI Challenge
description:
Hey there, Figmers! ✌️


100 Daily UI Challenge is a free library of products, elements and screens. You can customise all of them by changing colours, shapes or elements.


Every day, I tried to come up with new idea that can be used for larger projects in the future, not only by me but by anyone else.


You can create some pretty awesome UI designs and create better products.


Get started making awesomeness!
